@startuml
!theme plain
title IBM CIS Logs to LogDNA Serverless Function

participant "COS Bucket" as COS
participant "Serverless Function" as Function
participant "LogDNA" as LogDNA
participant "Archive Bucket" as Archive

COS -> Function : Trigger (New object created)
activate Function

Function -> COS : Download log file
COS --> Function : Return zipped log file

Function -> Function : Unzip and parse JSON

loop For each batch of 5000 logs
    Function -> LogDNA : Send logs
    LogDNA --> Function : Confirm receipt
end

Function -> Archive : Copy log file
Archive --> Function : Confirm copy

Function -> COS : Delete original log file
COS --> Function : Confirm deletion

deactivate Function
@enduml